Login to get authentication token

Example Response:
```json
{
    "access_token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
    "token_type": "bearer",
    "user": {
        "id": "67f967656557d4f1034a3c9f",
        "name": "John carter",
        "email": "john@example.com"
    }
}
```

Analyze a document

Example Response:
```json
{
    "document_id": "1",
    "summary": "TRADEMARK ASSIGNMENT...",
    "key_points": [
        "BETWEEN Assignor and Assignee...",
        "The Assignee will pay to the Assignor..."
    ],
    "risks": [
        "The Assignor is not aware of any competing claims..."
    ],
    "entities": [
        {
            "name": "Trademark Assignment",
            "type": "person",
            "mentions": ["Found in document"]
        }
    ],
    "model": "document-analyzer"
}
```

