request.description:
Chat with a document

Example Response:
```json
{
    "document_id": "1",
    "response": "I found the following relevant information in the document:\n\n1. TRADEMARK ASSIGNMENT...",
    "messages": [
        {
            "role": "user",
            "content": "What is the purpose of this document?"
        },
        {
            "role": "assistant",
            "content": "I found the following relevant information..."
        }
    ]
}
```
